General Information
===================

This is Summer version 0.1.0. Summer is a library that lets a developer quickly
and easily create applications that can automatically download multimedia files
from webfeeds, or, in other words, podcast clients and broadcatching
applications.

Summer is free software, released under the LGPL 2.0.

The official webpage is http://wrya.net/services/trac/summer There you can
report bugs, get the latest development code, and read documentation.

You can use the mail list at <summer@lists.wrya.net>. There's a web interface
for it at http://wrya.net/services/mailman/listinfo/summer

Note that this is a very early version of the library, and that it will contain
bugs and lack featues. Please report any errors you find.

